    "The PSO algorithm is developed by the behavior of social organisms like a flock of birds.",
    "The procedure starts with the generation of random solutions, called particles.",
    "The generations are then modified to find the optimal solution.",
    "The set of particles, called swarm, moves throughout the search space with a flexible velocity and retains the best location it has found.",
    "Each particle is capable of modifying its velocity vector to find the optimal location 44, 51, 54."
